{"tid":673441,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"華納暗黑版《魔幻森林》Andy Serkis執導","createTime":"2018-05-22T00:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T12:17:12.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18dd91c2cc080f170b75fe2fe86e91f4617f2642","tid":673441,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:02:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SyPWDGThH9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSyPWDGThH9c&d=Cf9YCzyxC9ID9a6tD1u72f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f4e644b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SyPWDGThH9c</a><br />\n<br />\n導演安迪席克斯是真人捕捉片的翹楚，他扮演過《魔戒》的咕嚕、《猩球崛起》的凱薩、威猛的《金剛》，在《STAR WARS：原力覺醒》中則是領袖史諾克。他在受訪時指出，真人版更接近真實世界，在森林中有許多不可測的驚險，「不會有小孩牽著動物的手唱歌跳舞的畫面。」安迪強調演技強大的演員群讓角色更加動人。"},{"pid":"d244f0126229d68b384649fcc0061ba071a7525e","tid":673441,"uid":105605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"咁快翻拍？"},{"pid":"ac7eb9abb5b45a28dbe1e3c93e773bcd43e68cb1","tid":673441,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d244f0126229d68b384649fcc0061ba071a7525e","tid":673441,"uid":105605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"咁快翻拍？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"華納版... 唔同"},{"pid":"40c23ac7278dcdf41b91af0cb8befa0fdc59a52a","tid":673441,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7eb9abb5b45a28dbe1e3c93e773bcd43e68cb1","tid":673441,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d244f0126229d68b384649fcc0061ba071a7525e","tid":673441,"uid":105605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"咁快翻拍？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"華納版... 唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"應該籌備咗幾年<br />\n又唔知迪士尼早一步拍緊"},{"pid":"b3b52a6619390ddf97667217ed7f6f1ae8f3fa0a","tid":673441,"uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-